					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5651448#post-3754343</guid>
				<title>A Midnight Ride</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5651448/scp-3886#post-3754343</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 31 Mar 2018 02:54:08 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ember16</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2952182</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So, after a complete rewrite, SCP-3886 is back, making it my still technically first and only SCP! Hopefully it is not awful.</p> <p>The tale ‘The Skeleton Dance’ (<a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/the-skeleton-dance">http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/the-skeleton-dance</a>) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522466178" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" >PeppersGhost</a></span>, while not required to understand this SCP, is highly recommended.</p> <p>And lastly, I want to thank all the great people who <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">tore this thing to shreds</span> made this SCP the best it could be on the critique board: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522466178" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522466178" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/galaxy-class" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3737554&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522466178" alt="Galaxy-Class" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3737554)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/galaxy-class" >Galaxy-Class</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522466178" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span> and many others!</p> 
				 	]]>
